article_title: Republicans lay out agendas at Sauk County event
article_text:
Baraboo, WI (53913)

Today

Thunderstorms likely this morning. Then the chance of scattered thunderstorms this afternoon. High 79F. Winds SSE at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 100%..

Tonight

Variable clouds with scattered thunderstorms. Low 63F. Winds SSE at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 60%.

og.description: Republicans with election aspirations took to the podium Thursday night in Baraboo during the Sauk County Republican Party’s annual Lincoln Day Dinner.
